Class DbxDataObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dropbox.core.DbxDataObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DbxAccountInfo, DbxAccountInfo.Quota, DbxAppInfo, DbxDelta, DbxDelta.Entry, DbxDeltaC, DbxDeltaC.Entry, DbxEntry

    public abstract class DbxDataObject
extends Object
    A common superclass for the data model classes. Contains a function to dump the data (for debugging purposes).
